column5: Cool, charming studio apartment in Central Austin bungalow duplex. Fully-equipped kitchen. Quiet and private, this apartment has its own shady backyard and its own off-street parking. Central Austin location close to bus stops. UT is 3 miles, downtown is 5.2 miles.  Nearby Burnet Road has trendy and highly-rated restaurants, fun bars and some of the best vintage shopping in Austin.
column8: Cool studio in groovy central Austin
